---
// By klok for the Glory of Jesus · 05-2026
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Quality Management System ISO 9001-2015 | Bufete Jurídico Pazos Chávez"
  description="ISO 9001-2015 Quality Policy of Bufete Jurídico Pazos Chávez S.C."
  lang="en"
>
  <Navbar />
  <main
    class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900"
  >
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-8">
          <a
            href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}en`}
            class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors mb-6"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
            </svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
          <h1
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >
            QUALITY
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-400">ISO 9001-2015</p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl border border-gray-700"
        >
          <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
            <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-8 leading-relaxed">
              <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-4">
                  1. OUR QUALITY POLICY
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-300">
                  At Bufete Jurídico Pazos Chávez S.C., we are committed to
                  providing Contact Center services for the Administration and
                  Recovery of Credit Portfolio in Extrajudicial and Judicial
                  Form, Notifications, as well as Customer Service that meet
                  the requirements of interested parties through compliance
                  with Management plans and strategies and quality objectives,
                  as well as the continuous improvement of the Quality
                  Management System within the applicable legal framework.
                </p>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-4">
                  2. OUR MISSION
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-gray-700/30 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
                  <p class="text-gray-300 italic">
                    "To provide professional services in accordance with
                    quality standards, within a framework of values,
                    integrating the capabilities and efforts of our
                    collaborators, in an environment of continuous improvement
                    that fosters the permanent development of those who
                    contribute to the objectives of the organization, for the
                    benefit of society."
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-4">
                  3. OUR VISION
                </h2>
                <div class="bg-gray-700/30 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
                  <p class="text-gray-300 italic">
                    "To consolidate ourselves as a leading company in the
                    provision of the services we offer; to achieve that our
                    work team integrates and consolidates around personal
                    ideals and objectives, and those of the organization, and
                    to build for our clients and suppliers an image of trust
                    grounded in the values that constitute our permanent
                    commitment."
                  </p>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-4">
                  4. TECHNOLOGICAL VISION
                </h2>
                <ol
                  class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3 text-gray-300 ml-4"
                >
                  <li>
                    For us, technology is one of the fundamental pillars of
                    our activities. We are convinced that the synergy between
                    human capital and the best technology will allow us to
                    achieve all our objectives more quickly.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    That is why at Bufete Jurídico Pazos Chávez S.C. we have
                    highly qualified personnel in this area, modern
                    communications and security equipment, and the best
                    systems to interact with clients and store information.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    The above allows us to guarantee each of our clients that
                    their information is safe in our hands, and that we will
                    use all technological innovations to offer them the best
                    results.
                  </li>
                </ol>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
